at interconnect data centers and ISPs across the country or across continen=
ts.
Here, our packet, still barely even a twinkle in its parents=E2=80=99 eyes =
on human timescale but nearly halfway through its packet-scale life, comes =
to its first fork in the road.
If it=E2=80=99s traveling to a destination in its own geographic region or =
on the same ISP (or an ISP with a peering agreement with its own), it might=
