<p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0;color: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;font-=
size: 16px;"><span>The switch reads the MAC Address within the ethernet fra=
me to figure out where to send the packet next, whether to another device o=
n the network or to a gateway router that will send it out into the </span>=
<strong>internet</strong><span>. The switch forwards the packet only to the=
 specific port needed to reach its destination, avoiding congestion and inc=
reasing efficiency in the network.</span></p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 20px 0=
;color: rgb(54,55,55);line-height: 26px;font-size: 16px;"><span>Let&#8217;s=
